headline: Ulta Beauty (ULTA): A Fresh Look at Valuation as Shares Continue Their Upward Trend
summary: Ulta Beauty (ULTA) shares have edged higher recently, climbing around 1% over the past day and gaining about 5% this week. Investors are taking note of the stock’s upward move, which is prompting a closer look at what is driving sentiment. See our latest analysis for Ulta Beauty. Ulta Beauty’s latest move builds on a remarkable stretch for the retailer, with strong price momentum this year as its share price climbed over 21% year-to-date and racked up a stellar 38.9% total shareholder return...
